---
title: Cal Smart Harissa Shrimp and Chickpea Stew with Buttered Ciabatta
description: Smoky and complex North African spices are combined with chili-garlic sauce to infuse this dish with intense flavours. Ciabatta points are perfect dippers for this visually appealing and wholesome stew!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-crevettes-et-de-pois-chiches-au-harissa-408b6c3c.jpg
